  "title": "Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise daily production activities to ensure targets, quality, and safety standards are met.</li><li>Coordinate with operators, technicians, and quality control teams to maintain smooth workflow.</li><li>Monitor machine performance, report issues, and support maintenance activities.</li><li>Ensure compliance with production schedules and workplace safety regulations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2–3 years of experience in a factory or production environment.</li><li>Good leadership, communication, and problem-solving skills.</li><li>Basic understanding of processes and machinery preferred.</li></ul>",
